('062384', 'ENGR', 'EGR', 'EMGT', '373', 'Technology Entrepreneurship', 'In this course you will master fundamental principles, then initiate, design and document actual new technology business enterprises.  Both the entrepreneurial and intrapreneurial business models will be covered.  Further, you will develop an understanding of the rewards, risks, goals, and techniques relating to start-up technology businesses, including how to create innovative strategies.', '2.00', '2.00', 'A'),
