('064922', 'UGRD', 'AS', 'PHSC', '197', 'Public Health Internship', 'Directed internship off-campus in public health-related activities or research, under the guidance of a qualified public health professional. Open to public health science majors with permission of faculty advisor or the Director of the Public Health Program. May be repeated for a limit of no more than 5 total PHSC 197 units.  P/NP.  Prerequisites: PHSC 1', '5.00', '1.00', 'A'),
