('065028', 'UGRD', 'AS', 'PHSC', '172', 'Management of Health Care Organizations', 'Explores the sociological and practical issues of operations, financing, and management in organizations providing services for people with health problems (organizations such as nursing homes and hospitals) or people with infirmities (organizations such as senior care centers and assisted living facilities).  Also listed as SOCI 172.', '5.00', '5.00', 'A'),
